num1=int(input("enter first number"))
num2=int(input("enter second number"))
num3=int(input("enter third number"))
total=num1+num2+num3
print(f'total is {num1}+{num2}+{num3}={total}')
average=(num1+num2+num3)/3
print(f'average({num1},{num2},{num3}) is {average:.3f}')

Output:
enter number3
enter number5
enter number7
total is 3+5+7=15
average(3,5,7) is 5.000
